fi.cebylfwk.component
Interface Entity

All Superinterfaces:
Renderable, Resource, Updateable
public interface Entity
extends Renderable, Updateable, Resource

Representation of the game object. Every game object must implement this interface. All entities will be registered to entitymanager.
